Public projects that are configured to be discoverable can be easily shared with users so they can begin consuming the micro-learning gamified training!

To share a project click on the `Share` button on the project admin page.
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)
Once the `Share` button is clicked the share information modal is displayed.
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)
Copy the url and share it with your trainees. When the link is visited, two things happen:

* The Progress and Ranking page for that project is displayed *AND*
* the project is automatically added to My Projects.

> **Important**
> The `Share` button is only displayed if the Project Visibility is configured to the `Discoverable on Progress and Ranking` option.
